text: Reiner Schilling (10 May 1943 - 15 October 2013) was a German wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle featherweight at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1943 births Category:2013 deaths Category:German male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of the United Team of Germany Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:People from Tuttlingen
